If backoffice is not loading after the deployment for the first time from the sap portal then follow the below steps:

Environment
SAP Commerce Cloud

Resolution
1. Go to your Commerce Cloud Portal of the specific environment.
2. In public endpoint, click on the backoffice to edit endpoint
3. Scroll down to the Filtering and Redirects section
4. Set the IP Filter Sets - Base Rule to Allow ALL
5. Save

Similar way update the other endpoints as per the need
